data.description: Welcome to Terra Bella.  This beautiful gated community is located in a premier location in Stone Oak.  Terra Bella offers gated entry, pool, cabana, walking trails, HEB within walking distance, many popular restaurants and a great part of the city to live in.  This amazing two story home offers 3388 square feet, 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, stunning rock fireplace, separate dining room, office, media room, upstairs laundry room, wood floors as well at a huge corner lot with many mature trees.  Located on a corner lot, this home is 100 feet from the pool and community park.  Seller recently replaces both gas water heaters and sprinkler control box.  Bring your buyers and enjoy this amazing home!!
